    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一台服务器既想要运行Nginx,又同时要运行Node.js？使用Nginx的反向代理轻松解决。<br><a id="more"></a></p>
<h2 id="如何使用nginx代理Node服务"><a href="#如何使用nginx代理Node服务" class="headerlink" title="如何使用nginx代理Node服务"></a>如何使用nginx代理Node服务</h2><p>在nginx的站点配置目录（ /etc/nginx/conf.d/ ）中新建一个虚拟主机 ( xxx.conf ), 粘贴下方代码</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div><div class="line">12</div><div class="line">13</div><div class="line">14</div><div class="line">15</div><div class="line">16</div><div class="line">17</div><div class="line">18</div><div class="line">19</div><div class="line">20</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">upstream nodejs &#123;</div><div class="line">    server 127.0.0.1:3000; # Node.js监听的地址及端口号</div><div class="line">    keepalive 64;</div><div class="line">&#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">server &#123;</div><div class="line">    listen 80; # Nginx监听端口</div><div class="line">    server_name freelion.me; # 绑定的域名</div><div class="line">    access_log /var/log/nginx/test.log; # 日志文件</div><div class="line">    location / &#123;</div><div class="line">        proxy_set_header X-Real-IP $remote_addr;</div><div class="line">        proxy_set_header X-Forwarded-For $proxy_add_x_forwarded_for;</div><div class="line">        proxy_set_header Host  $http_host;</div><div class="line">        proxy_set_header X-Nginx-Proxy true;</div><div class="line">        proxy_set_header Connection &quot;&quot;;</div><div class="line">        proxy_pass      http://nodejs;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">    &#125;</div><div class="line"></div><div class="line">&#125;</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
